products.name: iPhone 13
products.description: As part of our efforts to reach carbon neutrality by 2030, iPhone 13 does not include a power adapter or EarPods. Included in the box is a USB‑C to Lightning Cable that supports charging and is compatible with USB‑C power adapters and computer ports.
